The paper deals with image restoration and recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of generative models and deep learning techniques suggests that it could also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also involves the use of adversarial and perceptual losses, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
